labels.shortDescription: AccountTriggerHandler - Prior to converting a lead, create an Account in ERP
labels.value:
Prior to converting a lead, an Account must be created in ERP. If your lead is associated with
an existing Account, please return to the previous screen and select "Attach to Existing" account.

Tips on Account creation-

If the Account you are attempting to create does not exist in NSC, and is located in an ERP country,
then please create the account in CWEB. The Account will appear in NSC in 24 hours
and you will be able to select it as "Attach to Existing" account when converting the Lead.


If the account you are attempting to create does not exist in NSC, and is located in a non-ERP country,
then please go to the “Account Request” tab in NSC and request for a new account.
Once Admin creates the new Account in NSC, you will be able to select it as "Attach to Existing" account when converting the Lead.
